RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT REASON_CODE, REASON_DESC FROM OLTMS_REASON WHERE MODULE_CODE ='LB' AND EVENT_CODE = 'VAMB' AND AUTH_STAT ='A' AND RECORD_STAT ='O' AND PROCESSING_REQD = 'Y' ORDER BY REASON_CODE

SELECT a.CONTRACT_REF_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT a WHERE a.BRANCH = nvl(?,GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH) AND a.MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND a.CONTRACT_STATUS in ('A','L') AND NOT EXISTS ( Select 1 from LFTB_MARGIN_REVN_ACTIVATED_CONT b where a.contract_ref_no = b.contract_ref_no AND NOT ( a.contract_status = 'A' AND b.contract_liquidated = 'Y' ) ) ORDER BY a.CONTRACT_REF_NO

RAD_SUMMARY.TITLE: LBL_VAMND
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: Branch IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT brn_code, brn_name, eoti_desc, time_level FROM (SELECT a.branch_code brn_code,a.branch_name brn_name, decode(b.end_of_input, 'N', 'Transaction Input', 'T','End of Transaction Input', 'F', 'End Of Financial Input', 'E','End of Day','B', 'Beginning of Day') eoti_desc,b.time_level time_level FROM sttm_core_branch a, sttm_core_branch_status b WHERE a.branch_code = b.branch_code and a.auth_stat = 'A' AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND a.branch_code IN (select branch_code from smvw_user_branches u where u.user_id = global.user_id) AND a.branch_code IN (select branch_code from smvw_consolidated_userrole r where r.user_id = global.user_id /*AND r.branch_code<> global.current_branch*/)) WHERE 1 = 1
